## 🆘 Quick Help Commands

```bash
# Current branch
git branch

# All branches
git branch -a

# Undo last commit (before push)
git reset --soft HEAD~1

# View commit history
git log --oneline -5

# See changes before commit
git diff

# Discard changes to a file
git checkout -- filename.txt

# Switch branch
git switch feature/team1-data-upload
```

